HEADWORD: jiggery-pokery
<hw>jiggery-pokery</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A verbal misrepresentation
intended to take advantage of a person in some way.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> trickery, hocus-pocus, slickness, hanky panky,
skulduggery, skullduggery.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

